name: 山城高岭(山城たかね)(Yamashiro Takane)/东方Project(東方Project)(Touhou Project)embedding
description:
Yamashiro Takane from Touhou Project 18 Unconnected Marketeers as the second stage.

Training Model: AbyssOrangeMix3 (AOM3)

The weight should not be too high, which is around 0.8

Recommended weight: 0.7~1.0; CFG Scale: 6~8

You can try different weights for different models.

You can try these words for the prompt:

key,

camouflage, camouflage_shirt, camouflage_skirt, camouflage_headwear

green_skirt, green_shirt,

green_hair, green_eyes, boots,

mountain, forest, trees

Without giving the camouflage indict, the output might be pure green clothes.

This is an embedding instead of a Lora.
